{"tid":544933,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"急！！有咩辦法先可以知自己有無口臭？","createTime":"2018-01-30T04:40:17.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-03T10:26:44.000Z","uid":39971,"like":9,"dislike":72,"uniUserReply":42,"replies":[{"pid":"d092e265e30c36cf1ee48b4e90bf28c0fb19fb36","tid":544933,"uid":39971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-30T04:40:17.000Z","msg":"唔好再建議向手板呵氣呢個方法 完全無撚用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我仲聽過一個方法 用口水奶一下手背 <br />\n等乾咗之後再聞 如果臭即係有口臭 <br />\n我試過 但每次都臭嘅 仲係街度搞到成手口水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我認真諗過之後發現呢個方法係痴撚線嘅 一定係無用嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我有一個實用嘅方法可以推薦 就係揾讀緊小學嘅細佬幫我聞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n雖然佢一開始會抗拒 但比粒lindor佢就氹掂<br />\n衹有親人先會比中肯評價 佢會直接講臭過屎坑<br />\n但呢個方法有局限性<br />\n<br />\n有無其他辦法可以知自己有無口臭！？<br />\n假設無註牙"},{"pid":"85ccefd67847c230bd14172b26539b010dd50081","tid":544933,"uid":8500,"like":118,"dislike":1,"score":117,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-30T04:41:28.000Z","msg":"叫細佬聞咁仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d16f9ce2b006732c14b387837964d964f224c80","tid":544933,"uid":22566,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-30T04:43:45.000Z","msg":"點一點口水係自己個鼻下面咪知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8426ea2b9b92fd9960530059d4cbca2bd6aa22c5","tid":544933,"uid":65743,"like":49,"dislike":3,"score":46,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-30T04:51:22.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">你合撚埋把口就無問題啦</span></span>"},{"pid":"bc59251d35ee99a3417a8f85ef238e0200005769","tid":544933,"uid":150881,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-30T04:53:22.000Z","msg":"有幾賤先可以叫親細佬做埋啲咁噁心嘅野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d54b7d2f1cd9db9f70a3c30a0976e221decebe7","tid":544933,"u